                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10164" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2561</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">269 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">立“腾云驾雾”之志，践“脚踏实地”之行——游戏科学公司破局3A游戏产业的战略创新实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Establish the ambition of &quot;living the clouds and fog&quot; and practice the journey of &quot;down-to-earth&quot; —— The Strategic Practice of Game Science Company in Breaking Through the 3A Game Industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐文秀，张渝知，闵闵然，李冰洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市游科互动科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">游戏科学公司；核心能力；蓝海战略；价值创新；愿景领导</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Game science company; Vision leadership; Core competencies; Blue Ocean Strategy; Value Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球游戏产业竞争激烈、3A游戏市场长期被欧美巨头垄断、国内单机游戏市场相对低迷的背景下，创新与突破成为国内游戏企业发展的关键。在此背景下，游戏科学公司制作上线《黑神话：悟空》并大获成功，该事件引发广泛热议，被誉为“开辟国产3A游戏的元年”。本案例聚焦游戏科学公司打造“具有世界品质，讲述中国故事”3A游戏的战略实践，深入剖析游戏行业供需特征，重点探讨了：初创企业如何利用核心能力构建可持续竞争优势，并通过价值创新开辟蓝海新市场，突破竞争困局；愿景领导如何支撑蓝海战略落地，以及动态能力如何持续守护“蓝海”。本案例旨在引导学员理解分析游戏科学公司成功开发《黑神话：悟空》的核心动因与经验，为初创公司在资源约束下构建可持续竞争优势，以及为数字娱乐产业公司的战略决策提供参考与启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Against the backdrop of fierce competition in the global gaming industry, the long-term monopoly of 3A game markets by European and American giants, and the relative sluggishness of the domestic single-player game market, innovation and breakthrough have become the key to the development of domestic gaming enterprises. In this context, Game Science successfully developed and launched&#160;Black Myth: Wukong, which sparked widespread discussion and is hailed as &quot;the first year of domestic 3A games&quot;. This case focuses on Game Science’s strategic practice of creating a 3A game that &quot;boasts world-class quality and tells Chinese stories&quot;, conducts an in-depth analysis of the supply and demand characteristics of the gaming industry, and focuses on exploring the following aspects: how startups can leverage their core capabilities to build sustainable competitive advantages, open up new blue ocean markets through value innovation, and break through competitive dilemmas; how visionary leadership supports the implementation of the blue ocean strategy; and how dynamic capabilities continuously safeguard the &quot;blue ocean&quot;. The purpose of this case is to guide students to understand and analyze the core motivations and experiences behind Game Science’s successful development of&#160;Black Myth: Wukong, and to provide references and insights for startups to build sustainable competitive advantages under resource constraints, as well as for strategic decision-making of digital entertainment industry companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">核心能力理论;蓝海战略;愿景领导理论;动态能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
